such special purpose shipments;

 Upon request by the committee, furnish reports, or cause reports to
be furnished, for each shipment pursuant to the applicable Special
Purpose Certificate;

 Mail to the office of the committee a copy of the bill of lading
for each Special Purpose Certificate shipment promptly after the
date of shipment unless other arrangements are made;

 Complete and return an application form for consideration of
approval as a canner, freezer, or other processor of potato
products;

 Certify to the committee and to the Secretary that potatoes
received from the production area for processing will be used for
